Symbol.Script_3D:
! Tea Cup.gsm
pen gs_cont_pen if gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_OFF then end if gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_SIMPLE then gs_resol = 6
if gs_shadow=0 then SHADOW OFF
H=B
HOTSPOT 0,0,0 HOTSPOT b/2,0,0 HOTSPOT 0,b/2,0 HOTSPOT -b/2,0,0 HOTSPOT 0,-b/2,0
HOTSPOT b/2+7/16*b,0,9/16*b
HOTSPOT b/2,0,9/8*b HOTSPOT 0,b/2,9/8*b HOTSPOT -b/2,0,9/8*b HOTSPOT 0,-b/2,9/8*b
Resol 2*gs_resol Material mat1 Cylind H/16, H/2 Addz H/16 Roty -90 Revolve 5, 360, 15, 0, H/2, 0, H, H/2, 0, H, H/2-H/16, 0, 0, H/2-H/16, 0, 0, H/2, 0 Material mat2 Addx H Revolve 5, 360, 15, 0, H/2, 0, H/16, H/2, 0, H/16, H/2-H/16, 0, 0, H/2-H/16, 0, 0, H/2, 0 Del 2
Addz H*7/8 Addx H/2 Roty 90 material mat1 Resol gs_resol Elbow (H/2)-(H/8), 180, H/16 Del 3 Material mat3 Resol 2*gs_resol Cylind Rnd(H/2)+H/2, H/2-H/16 del 1 End
Symbol.Script_2D:
!!Tea Cup.gsm
pen gs_cont_pen FILL gs_fill_type
POLY2_B 5, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, b/2, 0, 1, -0.0, 0.0, 900, b/2, 180, 4001, 0.0, 0.0, 900, b/2, 180, 4001
LINE2 b/2,0,b/2+7/16*b,0
HOTSPOT2 0,0 !! Default Hotspot
HOTSPOT2 b/2,0 HOTSPOT2 0,b/2 HOTSPOT2 -b/2,0 HOTSPOT2 0,-b/2 HOTSPOT2 b/2+7/16*b,0
Symbol.Script_1D: ! const values for parameter: gs_detlevel_3D_m DLEV3D_OFF = 0 DLEV3D_SIMPLE = 1 DLEV3D_DETAILED = 2 DLEV3D_DRAFT = 3
Symbol.Script_VL:
call "FM_types" parameters all
values{2} "gs_detlevel_3D_m" DLEV3D_DETAILED, `Детальный`, DLEV3D_SIMPLE, `Простой`, DLEV3D_OFF, `Откл.` values "gs_resol" range [3,)
if gs_cont_pen=0 then parameters gs_cont_pen=7 if gs_fill_pen=0 then parameters gs_fill_pen=91
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_SIMPLE then hideparameter "gs_resol" if gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_OFF then hideparameter "gs_resol", "gs_shadow"
parameters a=b+7/16*b parameters ZZYZX=9/8*b lock "a", "ZZYZX" hideparameter all "A", "B", "ZZYZX"
